title: Infernal Syndra Skin concept

embed.description: I had so much fun with this little project and i plan on doing more!

body:
So i was bored and decided to make a skin concept, I went through the process of concepting the skin and then to modelling and making a fan a splash :) i hope you guys like it! just wanted to share. I also have it posted it on Reddit. 
REDDIT POST: https://www.reddit.com/r/leagueoflegends/comments/68q0wl/infernal_syndra_skin_concept/?st=j2b3aick&sh=af774563
The concept is attached to this post. :D

replies.body: Wow!  That is really cool. Great job!
